#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "Dobrodošli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Welcome to &umbrello; an &UML; diagram tool that can support you in the "
"software development process. Especially during the analysis and design "
"phases of this process, &umbrello; will help you to get a high quality "
"product. &UML; can also be used to document your software designs to help "
"you and your fellow developers."
msgstr ""
"Dobrodošli v &umbrello; &UML; orodje za diagrame, ki vam lahko pomaga pri "
"procesu razvoja programske opreme. Zlasti med fazo analize in načrtovanja "
"tega procesa vam bo &umbrello; pomagal do visokokakovostnega izdelka. &UML; "
"se lahko uporablja tudi za dokumentiranje načrtov vaše programske opreme, da "
"pomaga. am in vašim kolegom razvijalcem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start working with UML you may create a new diagram from one of the "
"following diagram types:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti delati z UML, lahko ustvarite nov diagram iz ene od "
"naslednjih vrst diagramov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"use-case-diagram\">Use Case Diagram</ulink></"
"emphasis> - show actors (people or other users of the system), use cases "
"(the scenarios when they use the system), and their relationships"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"use-case-diagram\">Diagram primerov uporabe</ulink></"
"emphasis> - prikažite akterje (ljudi ali druge uporabnike sistema), primere "
"uporabe (scenarije, ko uporabljajo sistem) , in njihove odnose"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"class-diagram\">Class Diagram</ulink></emphasis> - "
"show classes and the relationships between them"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"class-diagram\">Diagram razreda</ulink></emphasis> - "
"prikažite razrede in razmerja med njimi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"sequence-diagram\">Sequence Diagram</ulink></"
"emphasis> - show objects and a sequence of method calls they make to other "
"objects."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"sequence-diagram\">Diagram zaporedij</ulink></"
"emphasis> – pokažite objekte in zaporedje klicev metod, ki jih napravijo "
"drugim objektom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"collaboration-diagram\">Collaboration Diagram</"
"ulink></emphasis> - show objects and their relationship, putting emphasis on "
"the objects that participate in the message exchange"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"collaboration-diagram\">Diagram sodelovanja</ulink></"
"emphasis> - prikažite predmete in njihov odnos, s poudarkom na objektih, ki "
"sodelujejo pri izmenjavi sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"state-diagram\">State Diagram</ulink></emphasis> - "
"show states, state changes and events in an object or a part of the system"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"state-diagram\">Diagram stanj</ulink></emphasis> - "
"prikažite stanja, spremembe stanja in dogodke v objektu ali delu sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"activity-diagram\">Activity Diagram</ulink></"
"emphasis> - show activities and the changes from one activity to another "
"with the events occurring in some part of the system"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"activity-diagram\">Diagram dejavnosti</ulink></"
"emphasis> - prikažite dejavnosti in spremembe iz ene dejavnosti v drugo z "
"dogodki, ki se zgodijo v nekem delu sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"component-diagram\">Component Diagram</ulink></"
"emphasis> - show the high level programming components (such as KParts or "
"Java Beans)."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"component-diagram\">Diagram komponent</ulink></"
"emphasis> - pokažite komponente programiranja na visoki ravni (kot so KParts "
"ali Java Beans)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"deployment-diagram\">Deployment Diagram</ulink></"
"emphasis> - show the instances of the components and their relationships."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"deployment-diagram\">Diagram razmestitve</ulink></"
"emphasis> – pokažite primerke komponent in njihove odnose."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"entity-relationship-diagram\">Entity Relationship "
"Diagram</ulink></emphasis> - show data and the relationships and constraints "
"between the data."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis><ulink url=\"entity-relationship-diagram\">Diagram razmerij med "
"entitetami</ulink></emphasis> – prikažite podatke ter razmerja in omejitve "
"med podatki."
